{{Infobox company | type = Private | name = Nfinity Athletic Corporation | founded = 2003 | location = [[Atlanta, GA]] | key_people = Tate Chalk ([[entrepreneur|Founder]]/[[President (corporate title)|President]]/[[Chief executive officer|CEO]]) | products = Women's Performance Footwear and Apparel | homepage = [http://nfinity.com/ Nfinity.com] }}
'''Nfinity''' is headquartered in [[Atlanta, Georgia|Atlanta]], [[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]], in the [[United States]]. Nfinity markets [[cheerleading]], [[basketball]], and [[volleyball]] shoes and apparel particularly for female athletes. Nfinity designs shoes for a group of female athletes who struggle to get the recognition they deserve, attempting to fit to the biochemical needs of female athletes to enhance athletic performance and lower the risk of injury.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nfinity.com/About-Nfinity/Our-Story|title=Our Story|website=www.nfinity.com|access-date=2016-10-24}}</ref>
